s entirely of programming code. Capable of moving freely in cyberspace."},{"version":"blue","text":"A POK\u00e9MON that consists entirely of programming code. Capable of moving freely in cyberspace."},{"version":"yellow","text":"The only POK\u00e9MON people anticipate can fly into space. None has managed the feat yet, however."},{"version":"gold","text":"It is a manmade POK\u00e9MON. Since it doesn't breathe, people are eager to try it in any environment."},{"version":"silver","text":"A manmade POK\u00e9MON that came about as a result of re\u00ad search. It is pro\u00ad grammed with only basic motions."},{"version":"crystal","text":"An artificial POK\u00e9MON created due to extensive research, it can perform only what is in its program."},{"version":"ruby","text":"PORYGON is capable of reverting itself entirely back to program data and entering cyberspace. This POK\u00e9MON is copy-protected so it cannot be duplicated by copying."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"PORYGON is capable of reverting itself entirely back to program data and entering cyberspace. This POK\u00e9MON is copy-protected so it cannot be duplicated by copying."},{"version":"emerald","text":"It is capable of reverting itself entirely back to program data in order to enter cyberspace. A PORYGON is copy- protected so it cannot be duplicated."},{"version":"firered","text":"Using the most advanced technologies, scientists finally succeeded in making the first artificial POK\u00e9MON."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"A POK\u00e9MON that consists entirely of programming code. It is capable of moving freely in cyberspace."},{"version":"diamond","text":"The world\u2019s first artificially created Pok\u00e9mon. It can travel through electronic space."},{"version":"pearl","text":"The world\u2019s first artificially created Pok\u00e9mon. It can travel through electronic space."},{"version":"platinum","text":"A man-made Pok\u00e9mon created using advanced scientific means. It can move freely in cyberspace."},{"v